{"tid":2183954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「十八區開花」遇襲警認案發前用電筒「閃人隻眼」令對方舒服啲 惹來公眾席譁然","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T12:05:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":51,"dislike":402,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e99ce4ef79f3d4f5e8ee59e4ce7f6a24a45ead","tid":2183954,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/IZVLBHL7DNDDJEILUWXF6A4O3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FIZVLBHL7DNDDJEILUWXF6A4O3I%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7le0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=8372816b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FIZVLBHL7DNDDJEILUWXF6A4O3I%2F&h=818a7462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/IZVLBHL7DNDDJEILUWXF6A4O3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年理工大學被警方圍攻期間，網上號召「十八區開花」聲援理工大學示威者，各區陸續有示威者聚集，其間防暴警於天水圍賞湖居公園內撲跌追捕示威者時，遭多人襲擊腳踢。警長捉緊其中一隻腳並脫去對方鞋子，最後將該「甩鞋男」拘捕，控以襲警罪，案件今日在屯門法院開審。聲稱遇襲警被指當日用電筒「閃人隻眼」，他回應指用電筒「閃」對方眼比長照「令對方舒服啲」。"},{"pid":"18b6937da19213bb584bb0d1aae84c9eca406db2","tid":2183954,"uid":61161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"歪理"},{"pid":"c4da85f22cb4323b8e102f53158267e9cd603bb1","tid":2183954,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4bd74847c1b096c7a0a1fa133aea9463a3a2c67","tid":2183954,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /